Syntax: knee <target>

Delivers a knee strike to an opponent, targeting the midsection or legs.
Knee is a Warrior-line combat skill handled by the Warrior attack system.
It is available to Warden-class characters and their remort descendants
(Knight, Swordsman, Crusader).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp knee kick bash headbutt
